      "writtenOn": "2018-11-02T17:42:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "TODO: This only needs to be done the first time. I was tempted to do it inside onStartIncrementalDecode, but I\u0027m guessing that it has to wait for the call to decodeFrame? It should perhaps be in the same block that fills.",
      "range": {
