      "lineNbr": 388,
      "author": {
        "id": 8223
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-11-04T01:23:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Similarly, we may be able to use fFrames[options.fFrameIndex] instead of fFrameConfig here, to get the frame bounds. If we no longer use fFrameConfig inside onIncrementalDecode, we wouldn\u0027t need to call this-\u003edecodeFrameConfig, and worry about whether that call belongs in oSID or oID, and how it interacts with short I/O...",
      "revId": "8a250dc152e4a93801f77cbcb19c2e490656b67b",
